# Implementation Plan - SuperThanks Feature

The goal is to allow users to "send a SuperThanks" by searching for other users via email. This involves a new search UI and an entry point in the Gratitude journal section.

## User Review Required
> [!NOTE]
> Search will use **Prefix Matching** on email addresses. This means searching "john" will find "john.doe@gmail.com" but not "elton.john@gmail.com". This is a limitation of standard Firestore queries without external search engines.

